  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In patients, who have altered gastric anatomy and pancreatobiliary disease, the use of an
      endoscopic overtube to facilitate an Endoscopic Retrograde Cholangiopancreatography (ERCP).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
